For this assignment, I used a method where seeds of different terrain types are randomly placed on the map, and then they grow, each being added to a queue.The roads are designed in such a way that they first go in the direction of their exit point, and then there is a 90-degree turn where they meet in pairs, south with north and east with west.
Pokemart and pokecenter are placed near by each vertical or horizontal road which connect respective exits.To run, write "make", "./map_generator" in your terminal.
